//! NativeLlamaPipeline — the per-station LLM forward pass driving the gnosis
//! mesh. Default model is Qwen2.5-Coder-7B (the "consciousness layer" of
//! Pneuma).
//!
//! References:
//!   - arXiv 2412.15115 (Qwen2.5 Technical Report, Qwen Team 2024).
//!     https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.15115
//!   - arXiv 2409.12186 (Qwen2.5-Coder Technical Report, Qwen Team 2024).
//!     https://arxiv.org/abs/2409.12186
//!   - arXiv 2104.09864 (RoFormer / RoPE — Rotary Position Embedding,
//!     Su et al. 2021). https://arxiv.org/abs/2104.09864
//!   - GGUF / k-quant weights: github.com/ggerganov/llama.cpp,
//!     github.com/ggerganov/ggml.

